Name: Battery power
Explanation: Total energy a battery can store in one time measured in mAh

Name: Clock speed
Explanation: Speed at which microprocessor executes instructions

Name: Dual sim
Explanation: Has dual sim support or not

Name: Screen height
Explanation: Screen Height of mobile in cm

Name: Screen width
Explanation: Screen Width of mobile in cm

Name: Talk time
Explanation: Longest time that a single battery charge will last when you are talking
